---
// Mini-STRC Hypothesis section
---
<section id="mini-strc" class="px-6 py-16 border-t border-white/5">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
      <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-neutral-400">Mini-STRC假说</h2>
      <span class="px-1.5 py-0.5 text-[10px] rounded bg-purple-500/20 text-purple-400 font-semibold">NEW</span>
      <span class="px-1.5 py-0.5 text-[10px] rounded bg-yellow-500/20 text-yellow-400 font-semibold">COMPUTATIONAL</span>
    </div>
    <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm mb-8 max-w-2xl">
      当前STRC基因治疗需要两个AAV载体，因为该基因（5325 bp）超过了单个AAV的
      包装上限（约4400 bp可用）。AlphaFold结构分析表明单载体方案或许可行。
    </p>

    <!-- The problem -->
    <div class="bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5 rounded-lg p-5 mb-6">
      <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-3">包装容量问题</h3>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-xs mb-4">
        <div class="flex-1">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-1">
            <span class="text-neutral-400">完整STRC cDNA</span>
            <span class="text-red-400 font-mono">5325 bp</span>
          </div>
          <div class="h-3 bg-white/5 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
            <div class="h-full bg-red-500/60 rounded-full" style="width:100%"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-xs mb-4">
        <div class="flex-1">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-1">
            <span class="text-neutral-400">AAV上限（含启动子/ITR）</span>
            <span class="text-yellow-400 font-mono">~4400 bp</span>
          </div>
          <div class="h-3 bg-white/5 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
            <div class="h-full bg-yellow-500/60 rounded-full" style="width:82.6%"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-xs">
        <div class="flex-1">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-1">
            <span class="text-neutral-400">Mini-STRC（预测）</span>
            <span class="text-green-400 font-mono font-bold">3984 bp</span>
          </div>
          <div class="h-3 bg-white/5 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
            <div class="h-full bg-green-500/60 rounded-full" style="width:74.8%"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- AlphaFold insight -->
    <div class="bg-white/[0.02] border border-purple-500/20 rounded-lg p-5 mb-6">
      <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-3">AlphaFold揭示的信息</h3>
      <p class="text-xs text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        AlphaFold对静纤毛蛋白结构的预测置信度沿蛋白质序列呈差异分布。
        N端区域（残基1-615）的置信度极低（pLDDT &lt; 50），表明该区域
        可能本质上是无序的，没有稳定的三维结构。功能核心从约第616个残基开始。
      </p>
      
      <!-- pLDDT profile visualization -->
      <div class="relative h-20 bg-black/30 rounded overflow-hidden mb-3">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-end">
          <!-- Simplified pLDDT bars -->
          <div style="width:6.3%;height:17%" class="bg-red-500/60" title="1-114: avg pLDDT 30.6"></div>
          <div style="width:1%;height:55%" class="bg-yellow-500/40" title="115-131"></div>
          <div style="width:6.8%;height:21%" class="bg-red-500/60" title="132-251: avg pLDDT 37.0"></div>
          <div style="width:3.3%;height:60%" class="bg-yellow-500/40" title="252-308"></div>
          <div style="width:4.5%;height:25%" class="bg-red-500/50" title="309-387: disordered"></div>
          <div style="width:3.5%;height:55%" class="bg-yellow-500/40" title="388-448"></div>
          <div style="width:2.1%;height:27%" class="bg-red-500/50" title="449-485: disordered"></div>
          <div style="width:0.6%;height:55%" class="bg-yellow-500/40" title="486-495"></div>
          <div style="width:6.8%;height:18%" class="bg-red-500/60" title="496-615: avg pLDDT 31.1"></div>
          <div style="width:3.8%;height:60%" class="bg-yellow-500/50" title="616-682"></div>
          <div style="width:22.1%;height:78%" class="bg-blue-500/60" title="663-1074: LRR domain"></div>
          <div style="width:39.2%;height:85%" class="bg-blue-500/70" title="1075-1775: C-terminal"></div>
        </div>
        <!-- Position 1659 marker -->
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 bg-red-500" style="left:93.5%;width:2px;height:100%;"></div>
        <div class="absolute top-0 text-[9px] text-red-400 font-mono" style="left:90%;">E1659</div>
        <!-- Cutoff line -->
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 border-l-2 border-dashed border-green-500/50" style="left:34.7%;height:100%;"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-1 text-[9px] text-green-400 font-mono" style="left:28%;">截断点</div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="flex justify-between text-[10px] text-neutral-500 mb-4">
        <span>1</span>
        <span>N端（无序）</span>
        <span>LRR结构域</span>
        <span>C端（功能核心）</span>
        <span>1775</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- What to remove / what to keep -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6">
      <div class="bg-white/[0.02] border border-red-500/10 rounded-lg p-4">
        <h3 class="text-xs font-semibold text-red-400 mb-2">删除区域（447个氨基酸，1341 bp）</h3>
        <ul class="text-xs text-neutral-400 space-y-1.5">
          <li><span class="font-mono text-neutral-500">23-114</span> N端无序区（pLDDT 30.6）</li>
          <li><span class="font-mono text-neutral-500">132-251</span> 无序区（pLDDT 37.0）</li>
          <li><span class="font-mono text-neutral-500">309-387</span> 无序环（pLDDT 38-47）</li>
          <li><span class="font-mono text-neutral-500">449-485</span> 无序环（pLDDT 47.5）</li>
          <li><span class="font-mono text-neutral-500">496-615</span> 大型无序区（pLDDT 31.1）</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-[10px] text-neutral-500 mt-2">所有区域pLDDT &lt; 50（无稳定结构预测）</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white/[0.02] border border-green-500/10 rounded-lg p-4">
        <h3 class="text-xs font-semibold text-green-400 mb-2">保留区域（1328个氨基酸，3984 bp）</h3>
        <ul class="text-xs text-neutral-400 space-y-1.5">
          <li><span class="font-mono text-neutral-500">1-22</span> 信号肽（分泌功能）</li>
          <li><span class="font-mono text-neutral-500">616-1074</span> LRR结构域（蛋白质相互作用）</li>
          <li><span class="font-mono text-neutral-500">1075-1775</span> C端（盖膜附着）</li>
          <li><span class="font-mono text-neutral-500">1659</span> Misha的变异位点（得以保留）</li>
          <li>功能核心中8个糖基化位点得以保留</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-[10px] text-green-400 mt-2 font-semibold">3984 bp可装入单个AAV（&lt;4400 bp上限）</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Precedent -->
    <div class="bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5 rounded-lg p-5 mb-6">
      <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-2">先例：微型肌营养不良蛋白</h3>
      <p class="text-xs text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
        这一方法有成熟的先例。肌营养不良蛋白基因（11,000 bp）太大，无法装入任何AAV。
        研究人员通过删除非必需的血影蛋白样重复序列，创造了"微型肌营养不良蛋白"，
        使其可以装入单个AAV。该成果目前正处于肌营养不良症治疗的III期临床试验阶段（Sarepta SRP-9001）。
        其原理相同：识别结构核心，删除无序/冗余区域，保留功能。迄今尚无人在STRC中尝试这一方法。
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Caveat -->
    <div class="bg-yellow-500/10 border border-yellow-500/20 rounded-lg p-4">
      <p class="text-xs text-neutral-300">
        <strong>重要提示：</strong>这是基于AlphaFold结构预测的计算假说，需要实验验证：
        mini-静纤毛蛋白能否正确折叠？能否定位至静纤毛顶端？
        能否形成横向顶端连接和盖膜附着？这些问题需要湿实验验证。
        但结构数据强烈提示N端区域可能是可删除的，单AAV Mini-STRC方案值得深入研究。
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
